content:
[[iftags -组件]]
[[module CSS]]
:root {
  --safe: 0,159,107;
  --euclid: 255,211,0;
  --keter: 196,2,51;
  --esoteric: 66, 66, 72;
  --机密: 66, 66, 72;
  --機密: 66, 66, 72;
}

.contain-class .class-text {
  color: transparent !important;
}

.contain-class .class-text::before {
  content: "{$object}";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  color: rgba(51,51,51,1) !important;
}

.text-part > .main-class::before {
    margin-right: 0;
}

.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part > .main-class::before,
.anom-bar-container.机密 .text-part > .main-class::before,
.anom-bar-container.機密 .text-part > .main-class::before {
  background-color: rgba(var(--{$object-color}),1);
  background-image: url("{$object-image}");
  -webkit-filter: invert(0);
  filter: invert(0);
  border-color: rgb(12,12,12);
}

.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part > .main-class,
.anom-bar-container.机密 .text-part > .main-class,
.anom-bar-container.機密 .text-part > .main-class {
  background-color: rgb(12,12,12);
  background: linear-gradient(30deg,
    rgb(var(--{$esoteric-color}),0.25) 0%,
    rgb(var(--{$esoteric-color}),0.25) 50%,
    rgb(var(--{$object-color}),0.25) 50%,
    rgb(var(--{$object-color}),0.25) 50%
  )
}

.anom-bar-container.esoteric .danger-diamond > .top-icon::before,
.anom-bar-container.机密 .danger-diamond > .top-icon::before,
.anom-bar-container.機密 .danger-diamond > .top-icon::before {
  background-color: rgb(var(--{$object-color}));
  background-image: url("{$object-image}");
  -webkit-filter: invert(0);
  filter: invert(0);
}

.anom-bar-container.esoteric .danger-diamond > .quadrants > .top-quad,
.anom-bar-container.机密 .danger-diamond > .quadrants > .top-quad,
.anom-bar-container.機密 .danger-diamond > .quadrants > .top-quad {
    background-color: rgb(66, 66, 72 ,0.15);
    background-color: rgb(var(--{$object-color}),0.25);
}

.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part > .main-class > .second-class > .class-text::before,
.anom-bar-container.机密 .text-part > .main-class > .second-class > .class-text::before,
.anom-bar-container.機密 .text-part > .main-class > .second-class > .class-text::before {
content: "{$object2}";
color: #333333;
font-size: 0;
font-size: {$hideObject2};
}

.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part > .main-class > .second-class > .class-text,
.anom-bar-container.机密 .text-part > .main-class > .second-class > .class-text,
.anom-bar-container.機密 .text-part > .main-class > .second-class > .class-text {
font-size: {$hideObject};
}

[[/module]]
[[/iftags]]

[[iftags +组件]]

将ACS版头上的项目等级栏分割开，以同时显示一个机密分级和一个常规项目等级。

[[[scp-4703|示例在此。]]]

原代码作者为 [[*user Woedenaz]]。调整自 [[*user Yossipossi]] 所写的SCP-4531。由 [[*user PeppersGhost]] 进行组件化。

添加如下语法以使用此组件：

> [[include :scp-wiki-cn:component:acs-peppo-split
> |object= keter
> |object-image= http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Aanomaly-class-bar/keter-icon.svg
> |object-color= keter
> |esoteric-color= 机密
> ]]

如果你想让它显示一半“Safe”或者一半“Euclid”，调整“object”、“object-image”和“object-color”的值，只需将“keter”修改为“safe”或“euclid”。
[[/iftags]]
